  "title": "🦅 Marketing Associate – No Office, Just Action 🚀",
  "description": "<p>🕒 Full-time<br />💰 Competitive earnings + uncapped commission<br />🌍 Travel • Team Bonding • Personal Growth • Real People Skills</p><p>Join us as a <strong>Corporate Brand Ambassador</strong> — where you’ll represent meaningful brands, grow with a motivated team, and pick up skills that you can carry anywhere in life </p><p><strong>This is a face-to-face role</strong> — you’ll be meeting business owners <em>directly at their offices</em> to introduce solutions, build relationships, and grow your presence in the market.</p><p><strong>🌟 What You’ll Be Doing:</strong></p><ul><li>Meet business owners at their offices to pitch products and services</li><li>Be the friendly face behind our brand presence</li><li>Connect, follow up, and build meaningful working relationships</li><li>Collaborate with your team to hit shared goals</li><li>Track your own performance and grow every step of the way</li></ul><p><strong>🙌 Who This Is For:</strong></p><ul><li>People who love people</li><li>Curious learners who are coachable and open to growth</li><li>Fun-loving spirits who enjoy team vibes, challenges, and real results</li><li>Individuals open to travelling for events, work trips & team getaways</li></ul><p><strong>🎁 What You’ll Get:</strong></p><ul><li>1-on-1 mentorship & full product training</li><li>Easy-to-learn sales systems that get results</li><li>Career progression + leadership development paths</li><li>A young, energetic team with no shortage of vibes</li></ul><p>📩 Ready to step into a role that grows <em>you</em> while growing a brand? Let’s go.</p>",
